"Cookie Setting\",\"label_gdpr_banner_deny\":\"I want to change my cookies settings\",\"label_gdpr_banner_only_required_cookies\":\"Only Required Cookies\",\"label_gdpr_banner_reject_all_cookies\":\"Reject All Cookies\",\"label_gdpr_banner_title\":\"Cookie Usage\",\"label_gdpr_banner_your_cookie_preferences\":\"Your Cookie Preferences\",\"label_gdpr_confirm\":\"Confirm\",\"label_gdpr_cookie_preferences\":\"Cookie Preferences\",\"label_gdpr_cookie_preferences_error\":\"Halaman Tidak Ditemukan\",\"label_gdpr_essential_cookies\":\"Essential Cookies\",\"label_gdpr_facebook\":\"Facebook\",\"label_gdpr_functional_cookies\":\"Functional Cookies\",\"label_gdpr_google\":\"Google\",\"label_gdpr_privacy_policy\":\"Privacy Policy\",\"label_gdpr_show_more\":\"Show More\",\"label_gdpr_social_media_cookies\":\"Social Media Cookies\",\"label_gdpr_third_party_cookies\":\"Third Party Cookies\",\"label_gdpr_tiktok\":\"Tiktok\",\"label_tos_agree\":\"Setuju\",\"label_tos_cancel\":\"Batal\",\"label_tos_close\":\"Tutup\",\"label_tos_consent_to_shopee_policies\":\"Simak Ketentuan Akun Shopee\",\"label_tos_later\":\"Nanti\",\"label_tos_privacy_policy\":\"Kebijakan Privasi\",\"label_tos_terms_of_service\":\"Syarat Layanan\",\"label_user_gdpr_data_processing_consent_title\":\"Allow Shopee to provide recommendations\",\"label_user_gdpr_title\":\"Data Processing Consent\",\"msg_gdpr_advertising_cookies\":\"Collect information about your activity on the site or browsing activity to present content more relevant to you and your interests.\",\"msg_gdpr_analytical_cookies\":\"Collect technical information about your visit and interactions with the platform in order to understand your use of the services and improve your user experience.\",\"msg_gdpr_banner_message\":\"We use cookies to provide you with a better shopping experience and to understand your needs better. If you do not want to accept cookies on our platform, please click on “I want to change my cookies settings” and turn off cookies for our website in your cookies setting\",\"msg_gdpr_confirm_success\":\"Cookie Preferences Updated\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_consent_banner\":\"We use cookies to improve your experience at Shopee. For more information access our \\n{{privacy_policy}}\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_preferences\":\"Manage your options or withdraw your consent on our \\\"Customize Cookie Setting\\\". Learn more about our {{privacy_policy}}.\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_preferences_error\":\"Halaman yang ingin kamu akses tidak tersedia.\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_preferences_first_paragraph\":\"We use cookies and similar tools (collectively referred to as \\\"cookies\\\") for the purposes described below. For each of the following purposes, you can choose to activate the cookies by checking the switch of the related slider.\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_preferences_second_paragraph\":\"Please note that, unless you are logged in, your choices will only be effective on the web browser and device that you are currently using.\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_preferences__BR\":\"Select “Cookie Setting” to manage your options. You may adjust your preferences or withdraw your consent any time. If you want to learn more about the different types of cookies that we use and how we use them, visit our {{privacy_policy}} here.\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_usage\":\"Shopee uses cookies to enable the functioning of the Site and to deliver personalized experience and advertising. By clicking “Accept all cookies”, you agree that Shopee and third parties place cookies on your device. If you click “Reject all cookies”, only essential cookies strictly necessary for the provision of the service will be used.\",\"msg_gdpr_cookie_usage__BR\":\"Shopee uses cookies and other similar technologies to enable customers to make purchases, to keep our site reliable and secure, to deliver a personalized shopping experience and personalized advertising. These cookies collect information about users, their behavior, and their devices. By clicking “Accept all cookies”, you agree that Shopee and certain third parties may place cookies on your device, which enable us to provide personalized content and an improved and personalized shopping experience that better suits your preferences. If you click “Reject all cookies”, we will only use the essential cookies that are strictly necessary for the provision of the service and that do not require your consent, and you will not receive access to certain features or personalized content.\",\"msg_gdpr_essential_cookies\":\"Essential to make our Platform usable by enabling basic functions such as page navigation and access to secure areas of our Platform. The use of these cookies does not require your consent.\",\"msg_gdpr_functional_cookies\":\"Enable certain Platform functions, collect information about your activities, and remember certain preferences and settings you specify on the platform.\",\"msg_gdpr_learn_more_about_cookies\":\"If you want to learn more about cookies and our use of cookies in connection with Shopee’s services, visit our {{privacy_policy}} anytime.\",\"msg_gdpr_social_media_cookies\":\"Collect information about your social media interactions with our website.\",\"msg_gdpr_system_error\":\"System error, please try again later\",\"msg_gdpr_third_party_cookies\":\"These cookies may be provided by third party analytics providers or for advertising purposes, but are only used for purposes related to our services.\",\"msg_non_gdpr_cookie_preferences_first_paragraph\":\"Kami menggunakan cookies dan sejenisnya untuk tujuan yang dijelaskan di bawah ini. Untuk setiap tujuan berikut, kamu bisa aktifkan cookies dengan klik tombol yang tersedia.\",\"msg_tos_agree_to_shopee_tos_and_privacy_policy\":\"Dengan melanjutkan, saya mengakui telah membaca dan menyetujui {{privacy_policy}} Shopee.\",\"msg_tos_logout_error\":\"Maaf, telah terjadi kesalahan\",\"msg_tos_mandatory_will_be_logged_out_after_cancel\":\"Mohon perhatikan bahwa jika kamu memilih 'Tutup', akunmu akan log out otomatis.\",\"msg_user_